### Create task (подставь PROJECT_ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "PASTE-PROJECT-ID",
  "title": "Design homepage",
  "description": "Hero, CTA, pricing",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### List tasks by project
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks?projectId=PASTE-PROJECT-ID

### Update task status (подставь TASK_ID)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/PASTE-TASK-ID/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "DONE" }

### Create subtask (подставь TASK_ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": "PASTE-TASK-ID",
  "title": "Write hero copy",
  "status": "TODO"
}

### List subtasks by task
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subtasks?taskId=PASTE-TASK-ID

### Update subtask status (подставь SUBTASK_ID)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subtasks/PASTE-SUBTASK-ID/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "IN_PROGRESS" }
